Lightning Talk: DALL-E C++ Guessing Game - Hendrik Niemeyer - C++ on Sea 2022
Slides: https://github.com/philsquared/cpponsea-slides/tree/master/2022

With DALL-E you can let a machine learning model generate pictures from text. I fed it C++ words and phrases and you have to guess what they are.
---

Hendrik Niemeyer 

I am C++ developer for the ROSEN group and a programming language learning enthusiast.
